The Commentary to Â§5G1.2 is amended in the last paragraph by striking the first three sentences and inserting:
"Subsection (a) applies if a statute (1) specifies a term of imprisonment to be imposed; and (2) requires that such term of imprisonment be imposed to run consecutively to any other term of imprisonment.
